overview: Sydney is an ace (asexual identifying individual) who goes on blind dates to appease her overbearing roommate and best friend, Rachel. She truly has no desire to date, but she's learned over the years that it's just easier to oblige her pushy friend, and at least sometimes she gets a good story out of it. Adam is a lonely writer eager to find "the one". How in the world did these two get matched? This is the story of their blind date.
tagline: Not the blind date they were expecting.
title: Ace Date
